WorkItem.Summary: I have sample 271 EDI file, but I am getting "0 is not a valid subelement separator in position 105 of the file"

Comments.Message:
There are too many characters in your ISA segment.  This is a fixed width segment, each element is expected to be fixed width.  See the specification [here](https://www.disa.org/apps/workbook/X12_October_2012/se/se_ISA.htm).

If you post the first line as a code snippet then it will retain your whitespace and we can identify which element is incorrect.
